ttom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">s=
hut down</a>=C2=A0in 2019 and its parent company=C2=A0<a href=3D"https://li=
nk.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/24088975.258366/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYnVzaW5=
lc3NpbnNpZGVyLmNvbS9tb3ZpZXBhc3Mtb3duZXItaGVsaW9zLWFuZC1tYXRoZXNvbi1maWxlcy=
